{"tid":463614,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣Check小腦萎縮症？","createTime":"2017-11-09T16:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T17:24:41.000Z","uid":76399,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"47328d6d8320382cde80a39fa5b40fc698ef4487","tid":463614,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:10:26.000Z","msg":"睇醫生Check就一定架啦，但係要排公立定係直接搵私家Check？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋Check一次洗唔洗過萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約一年前我開始行路果陣會失平衡( 唔太嚴重嘅)，同埋企定定唔郁都會向左右郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔知係純粹自己平衡感差定係點，但我都想Check下等自己有個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有冇巴打對依方面有認識可以解答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e9a448f210cf1ae4009083adc93aa723ca4a81","tid":463614,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:17:49.000Z","msg":"交代返先，今年20歲<br />\n同埋依個月開始Feel到隻左手開始有啲震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋心跳得好快<br />\n我唔肯定隻手震係關心跳事定點，但已經開始做下運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，希望可以健康啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b9957e4a644d8b197e512241db378566d0e5a3","tid":463614,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe72a2519fd085601b5fe30c1c6d64461282e07","tid":463614,"uid":76399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fcf7b6748d72e44b0b831475b4f4b32e72eb2903","tid":463614,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:29:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fc113250b6ae0d90e