gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961fe7d72ded0dc43a5275887d2e645142921872","tid":463614,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"rip<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.healthsmart.com.hk/article/issues/I120382.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthsmart.com.hk%2Farticle%2Fissues%2FI120382.aspx&d=bh3RZ%2BlsTOrqm6zfbvEFy%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d072744a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.healthsmart.com.hk/article/issues/I120382.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"58f7d8770720da04bc74dacc6fdb1b707aa7c5f5","tid":463614,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇醫生Check就一定架啦，但係要排公立定係直接搵私家Check？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋Check一次洗唔洗過萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約一年前我開始行路果陣會失平衡( 唔太嚴重嘅)，同埋企定定唔郁都會向左右郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔知係純粹自己平衡感差定係點，但我都想Check下等自己有個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有冇巴打對依方面有認識可以解答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔係血糖低渣</blockquote><br />\n屌，Check一Check，血糖低D症狀又幾似，因為我不嬲都冇食早餐既習慣，同埋午餐食無定時/有時食個包就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我又唔肯定自己係唔係血糖低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，搵日搵家庭醫生睇下先"},{"pid":"aa24355f5205d679c39ac6387cdb160d9eb1cbcf","tid":463614,"uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>交代返先，今年20歲<br />\n同埋依個月開始Feel到隻左手開始有啲震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋心跳得好快<br />\n我唔肯定隻手震係關心跳事定點，但已經開始做下運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，希望可以健康啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係左手？右手呢？<br />\n震成點？<br />\n手腳會唔會冇力？冇感覺？<br />\n睇野有冇重影？<br />\n行路企唔穩？<br />\n食野有冇問題？"},{"pid":"a0a2769b49a55fd0219092ef1e44b15f52edcaa8","tid":463614,"uid":6755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:38:47.000Z","msg":"一公升眼淚"},{"pid":"9265a706f40b371fd2dadb902652cc1d55e07888","tid":463614,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>rip<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.healthsmart.com.hk/article/issues/I120382.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthsmart.com.hk%2Farticle%2Fissues%2FI120382.aspx&d=bh3RZ%2BlsTOrqm6zfbvEFy%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d072744a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.healthsmart.com.hk/article/issues/I120382.aspx</a></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係要照下個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打知道幾錢一次同埋搵邊間照好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281f38f6e736e52ec980b4bb63d9b4e0b3ead04c","tid":463614,"uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:40:12.000Z","msg":"你之前頭痛？宜家仲有冇？"},{"pid":"7e8eb9d62e57d3cc8d52d5438054664aca3236ab","tid":463614,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇醫生Check就一定架啦，但係要排公立定係直接搵私家Check？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋Check一次洗唔洗過萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約一年前我開始行路果陣會失平衡( 唔太嚴重嘅)，同埋企定定唔郁都會向左右郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔知係純粹自己平衡感差定係點，但我都想Check下等自己有個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有冇巴打對依方面有認識可以解答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔係血糖低渣</blockquote><br />\n屌，Check一Check，血糖低D症狀又幾似，因為我不嬲都冇食早餐既習慣，同埋午餐食無定時/有時食個包就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我又唔肯定自己係唔係血糖低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，搵日搵家庭醫生睇下先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以試下屋企單腳平衡企你度得下點，如果叮樣平衡力 ok 嘅話，好大機會血糖偏低。有時太趕冇食野/太大壓力 feel 唔到肚餓都會搞到血糖低，然後行路跌跌撞撞咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca63fe9285a5b9e88c1b3348e0b3a197e2234015","tid":463614,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>交代返先，今年20歲<br />\n同埋依個月開始Feel到隻左手開始有啲震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋心跳得好快<br />\n我唔肯定隻手震係關心跳事定點，但已經開始做下運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，希望可以健康啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係左手？右手呢？<br />\n震成點？<br />\n手腳會唔會冇力？冇感覺？<br />\n睇野有冇重影？<br />\n行路企唔穩？<br />\n食野有冇問題？</blockquote><br />\nSor講錯左，應該係右手震，左手好似冇<br />\n1.震既程度係D手掌位會跟心跳咁微微震，唔係話震到人地都睇得出<br />\n2.咩叫做重影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.唔會冇力呀，亦都唔會冇感覺<br />\n4.行路會間唔中向左右搖囉，我個人覺得唔太嚴重。不過企定唔郁都會有D平衡差(向前郁)既感覺<br />\n5.食野完全冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045893a58e771bac8cd02c598b8a35c36cef782b","tid":463614,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你之前頭痛？宜家仲有冇？</blockquote><br />\n間唔中會頭痛囉，不過都係同一個位痛。<br />\nTouch wood，依排冇頭痛"},{"pid":"450651d71dfd3e08d00ec7dde1925bd5df4d703b","tid":463614,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>交代返先，今年20歲<br />\n同埋依個月開始Feel到隻左手開始有啲震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/