":2462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲叫捱夜太多  我建議你照下條腸先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無知一問 關條腸咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db9dfe37bda5612547016633054ab93d7e525cb","tid":463614,"uid":154255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔夠訓姐 我都有你所講既病徵 <br />\n日日訓3~4小時"},{"pid":"7771c011d3910119f60c56cd0e604cb18f4c981d","tid":463614,"uid":2462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"樓豬 我就冇行路失平衡<br />\n但你講既企定定會前後左右郁 我都有<br />\n等mtr等巴士 或者合埋眼洗頭個陣更明顯<br />\n你有機會同我一樣係耳水不平衡<br />\n好小事 冇得醫 最多食止暈藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果陣我去睇醫生 佢叫我合上眼行路<br />\n同埋合上眼比人前後左右都輕輕推下<br />\n好似推不倒翁咁<br />\n如果合上眼行到直線 同埋又冇比人推跌到<br />\n應該唔大問題<br />\n至於心跳 訓得少 訓得差都會心悸架<br />\n<br />\nCheck下點都穩鎮d 比自己個安心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835e9bf2943cc69d5f443cfdcb9313a1c117a46c","tid":463614,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T19:26:43.000Z","msg":"樓上個個識少少扮代表，信一成都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽我講，做檢查一定係私家做，公立等幾年<br />\n<br />\n你個情況要搵腦科醫生睇<br />\n其實求其上網搵一個已經夠做<br />\n但如果想要品質保證既，我會搵大學醫院教授睇私家症"},{"pid":"b7c523663354c0c4df50ac5c76c9a2a076df6c44","tid":463614,"uid":20811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T20:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢啲叫捱夜太多  我建議你照下條腸先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無知一問 關條腸咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點睇佢都係似 食無定時 訓又無定時食親9成垃食物，香港過緊美國時區，照肝照腸先就岩，有排都未到個腦"},{"pid":"42590afe9c4327878250e4f9f6a55ce20fa00a65","tid":463614,"uid":131926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T21:32:57.000Z","msg":"要照磁力共振 應該都唔會平 但為左健康照照佢"},{"pid":"661052ec9051a1353fd2c606554be1ea5b0e88d8","tid":463614,"uid":2462,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T21:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上個個識少少扮代表，信一成都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽我講，做檢查一定係私家做，公立等幾年<br />\n<br />\n你個情況要搵腦科醫生睇<br />\n其實求其上網搵一個已經夠做<br />\n但如果想要品質保證既，我會搵大學醫院教授睇私家症</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個陣我長期頭痛頭暈<br />\n我keep住1,2星期就去睇一次醫生<br />\n有次頂唔順 我去醫生到話要照腦<br />\n叫佢寫referral比我去照<br />\n個醫生我由細睇到大<br />\n佢話照腦閒閒地過萬 叫我唔洗衝動擔心<br />\n做左d簡單測試先<br />\n覺得我有問題先會寫紙比我去照<br />\n<br />\nd測試就係我打果d 你估我自己9up出黎？<br />\n好心幫下樓主又要比你屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d753dde8e1ced5423144562245920e3356ee6b75","tid":463614,"uid":2462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T21:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上個個識少少扮代表，信一成都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽我講，做檢查一定係私家做，公立等幾年<br />\n<br />\n你個情況要搵腦科醫生睇<br />\n其實求其上網搵一個已經夠做<br />\n但如果想要品質保證既，我會搵大學醫院教授睇私家症</blockquote><br />\n而且我都有叫樓主去check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦無話佢100%係冇問題/有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c64246ea2f99879934ad95472927b700774028","tid":463614,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓上個個識